_:Nc73a2a69d37c44a89b40d8ca8ffb0e51 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Marcus Bell is Director of the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/office-for-equality-and-opportunity\">Office for Equality and Opportunity</a> in Cabinet Office, having been Director of the Race Disparity Unit since 2016.</p>\n\n<p>Marcus is a career civil servant, with a background mainly in social policy. He previously worked in the Department for Education, Ministry of Justice, and Ministry of Housing, Communities &amp; Local Government.</p>\n\n<p>Marcus was awarded the OBE for public service in the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/new-year-honours-list-2023-cabinet-office\">2023 New Year’s Honours List</a>.</p>\n" .
